            "loreEntryElements": [
                {
                    "@id": "/lore_entry_elements/01J21J29J3SS15YBMEYKNFMYEA",
                    "@type": "LoreEntryElement",
                    "id": "01J21J29J3SS15YBMEYKNFMYEA",
                    "loreEntryElementType": {
                        "@id": "/lore_entry_element_types/01GR6AENPX6HQP8G16KNV7BNA2",
                        "@type": "LoreEntryElementType",
                        "id": "01GR6AENPX6HQP8G16KNV7BNA2",
                        "reference": "FLAVOR_TEXT",
                        "subject": "Flavor Text"
                    },
                    "text": "The sound of the horn stirred them from their slumber as the white shadows emerged from the woods."
                },
                {
                    "@id": "/lore_entry_elements/01J21J29KPZQP9QX6PJZWZ14GK",
                    "@type": "LoreEntryElement",
                    "id": "01J21J29KPZQP9QX6PJZWZ14GK",
                    "loreEntryElementType": {
                        "@id": "/lore_entry_element_types/01GR6AE2ZSVVYP6SDJXN8Q5DVF",
                        "@type": "LoreEntryElementType",
                        "id": "01GR6AE2ZSVVYP6SDJXN8Q5DVF",
                        "reference": "STORY",
                        "subject": "Story"
                    },
                    "text": "Baaaaaaaaaaaahm! Baaaaaaaaaaaahm! I sound my great horn with all my might.\nTo your stations, to battle, o valiant guard!\nBe proud, though your hands be war-weary and scarred!\nAll around us, the resistance takes flight.\nTo your stations, to battle, o valiant guard!\nAnd brace both your bodies and hearts for the fight.\nAll around us, the resistance takes flight.\nFight for each furlong, and fight for each yard!\nAnd brace both your bodies and hearts for the fight.\nRaise to the sky shining spear and bright sword!\nFight for each furlong, and fight for each yard!\nThough the battle rages on through the dark of the night.\nRaise to the sky shining spear and bright sword!\nAnd call from your soul all the strength of the light.\nThough the battle rages on through the dark of the night.\nFight on, 'til dawn breaks over glorious reward.\nBaaaaaaaaaaaahm! Baaaaaaaaaaaahm! Nothing like a few verses to get warmed up and lift your spirits a bit, especially considering what we can see coming towards us in the mist up ahead.\n\nGulrang stands beside me, wrapped up in a fur-trimmed coat, her long dreads blowing in the wind. She raps my chest with her gloved hand, as though to bring me back to the present, but the sound of metal on stone is barely audible through the blizzard. I'm here, Gul, I say simply. I place my horn back in my marble compartment, looped around my shoulder, and look at the defenses. The earthen fort that we grew out of the ground using Alteration gives us a certain advantage, but it won't hold up indefinitely against the Belisenki assault. The ramparts of the fortified town are covered with troopers, and the officers are starting to issue their orders. The fortress contains about 50 soldiers, who are running to respond to the alarm I've just sounded. I suppose it's no longer time for poetry… but for the song of ringing steel."
                },
